The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | KKR request to CAB
                                                   KKR request to CAB
                      
	lThe Cricket Association of Bengal, on Saturday, received the Kolkata Knight Riders letter requesting the state association for access to the Eden Gardens facilities for their fitness camp.         
	KKR will be holding a two-day camp on Wednesday and Thursday at the Eden which the local players are likely to attend.         
	CAB joint secretary Biswarup Dey said: We received KKRs letter today (Saturday) and we have given our consent to their request. A written confirmation will be issued later.                                                                                                                       
